{"id": "1422544800514703502", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "108392615644278784", "author_name": "alistiel", "author_bot": false, "content": "she's one of those characters that does a lot of stuff that's shiny and distracting, a bit like a real street magician, but basically none of those things are \"survive 150% of my HP in incoming damage,\" \"turn target character's entire game plan,\" or \"instantly massacre everything in my field of view,\" and those things become concerningly relevant when you take 1500 damage every turn for the next six battles", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T11:25:10.047000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422333170032050238", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422584905719877758", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm gonna guess you are newer.\n\nIn Arc 2 rules her portrait is amazing. So you can restart a lot to try and get her portrait or wait for purple rings to get it.\n\nShe also is a tech unit to get rid of bad state cards. So bosses that put negative cards in your hand, you can use cassiah to dispose of them.", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T14:04:31.873000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["343685190654099457"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422333170032050238", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1422585422542016533", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "The devs made Cassiah more viable when they removed the turn limit in Arc 2.\n\nYou can Cassiah cheese and get a boss to do like 1 damage per hit with her portrait. But it takes a few turns to get there.", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T14:06:35.093000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["108392615644278784"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422544800514703502", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
