{"id": "1422682946309193910", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "type": 19, "author_id": "343685190654099457", "author_name": "noevd", "author_bot": false, "content": "okay maybe i have yet to see “take 1500 damage every turn” experience\n\nive just been using casiah with ramona to spam ramona’s queen sword (deal dmg 3 times each instance dmg dealt increase temp str +2 and each time card played adds +1 instance) i remember killing this one enemy that had 2000 health in turn 1 because i roused her and i had 5 of those cards in my extra turn deck arithmetica cost was 3 ( - 1 cuz of rouse so 2) but i had arithmetica orison on her so it basically cost 1, dealt like 2500 in all including the cards played before extra", "timestamp": "2025-09-30T20:34:06.571000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["108392615644278784"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1422544800514703502", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
